::Shredder::

Shredder turns around, looking at the ship. "Let's get working on fixing it," 
he says to the rest of the Destrons there.

He flies off toward the ship, recieving Datatron's transmission. "Uh, I think 
Magmatron already has the planet," he replies, "Going there would be useless."
